<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verification Code</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f8f8; margin:
      0; padding: 0; } .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px
      auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } h1 { color: #333333;
      font-size: 24px; } p { color: #555555; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;
      } .code { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #4caf50;
      background-color: #f1f1f1; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; display:
      inline-block; } .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #999999; margin-top:
      20px; } .footer a { color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Please Verify Your Email Address</h1>
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for initiating the sign-in process. To complete the sign-in,
        please use the 6-digit code below:
      </p>

      <p class="code">{{verification_code}}</p>

      <p>
        Please enter this code on the website where you started the sign-in
        process. The code will expire in 10 minutes, so make sure to use it
        soon.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you did not request this email or need help, please contact our
        support team at
        <a href="mailto:{{support_email}}">{{support_email}}</a>.
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          If you’re having trouble, you can also visit our
          <a href="{{site_host}}/support">support page</a>
          for more assistance.
        </p>
        <p>
          This email was sent to
          {{email}}. If this wasn’t you, please ignore this email.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>